<p>Dave and John start today&rsquo;s show by sharing some very useful tips and tricks that you can use in the Finder. Then it&rsquo;s off to the mailbag to discuss topics including how to better manipulate PDFs, troubleshooting a pixelated Mac display, Calendar sharing, and even a discussion about DMCA notices received from your ISP. Then it&rsquo;s Cool Stuff Found including tips for Safari, navigating traffic and and iOS settings. All of this and a LOT more on today&rsquo;s episode. Download now&hellip; it&rsquo;s free!</p>
